comment4.text=\r\n\ Return\ the\ display\ value\ (that\ is,\ the\ current\ value\r\n\ as\ a\ two-digit\ String.\ If\ the\ value\ is\ less\ than\ ten,\r\n\ it\ will\ be\ padded\ with\ a\ leading\ zero).\r\n
